HEADWORD: liven
<hw>liven</hw> <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>to make lively; -- sometimes used
with <ptcl>up</ptcl>; <as>as, to <ex>liven</ex> up the party with some
music</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> enliven, liven up, make lively, invigorate,
animate.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

